Upgrade Model:
Increase Damage and Range per level. Reload time and Power Cost typically remain constant unless higher-level data show otherwise.

Implementation Notes:

Guided weapon type — uses missile flight model (speed 80 m/s, turn rate 30 deg/s).

Apply standard hit, crit, and armor rules upon impact; subject to normal target Avoidance.

Consumes Power Cost when missile is fired, not on impact.

One reload timer per mount; cannot fire again until missile returns to ready state.

Use 180° firing arc for lock-on cone; enforce ship-class eligibility (Line only).

