Uses proximity detonation model: each projectile explodes near target within 10–15 m, applying splash damage.

Reduced Armor Piercing reflects anti-missile/light-craft specialization.

Accuracy 300 enables wide-area saturation but reduces long-range hit consistency.

Maintain independent reload timers for multiple mounts.

Restricted to Line-class hardpoints — enforce in Store and Fitting UI.

Consider optional visual effect: persistent flak bursts for area defense feedback.

